<!--
First Motive Axol MuJoCo model.

Authored by First Motive (Almond Bot ships no MJCF): compiled from the vendored
axol.urdf (almond-bot/axol, MIT) with `mujoco.MjModel.from_xml_path` +
`mj_saveLastXML`, then normalised (meshdir=meshes, model name, weightless option,
one position actuator per joint). Meshes are the upstream STLs, copied alongside.

Unlike the OpenArm and SO101 sim models — vendored under external/ and referenced
by absolute path in fm_sim_models/models.py — this one is committed into this
package's share because Axol has no upstream MJCF to vendor. Regenerate by
re-running the compile against a newer axol.urdf pin.

Joints: {left,right}_{s1,s2,s3,e1,e2,w1,w2}_0 (14 total, names match the
description + ros2_control exactly). Grippers are fixed in the URDF (no DOF).
-->
